##  About this Project
Artelyes is a website dedicated to the presentation and publication of the works of art of Mr Elyes Tayeb Lamine<br/>
<a href="https://lyric-boot.netlify.app/">live demo </a>


## Installation

To clone and run this application, you'll need [Git](https://git-scm.com) , [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/en/download/) [Yarn](https://yarnpkg.com/) installed on your computer. From your command line:

```bash
# Clone this repository
$ git clone https://github.com/TadjerouniMohamedAdel/artelyes.git

# Go into the repository
$ cd artelyes

# Install dependencies
$ yarn install

# Run the app
$ yarn start
```
